The following list is an enumeration of all pages of <%= @book.title %>.
</p>

<p><strong>Basic Pages:</strong></p>
<table class="contentstable" align="center"><tbody><tr>
  <td width="50%">
    <p class="biglink"><a class="biglink" href="whatsnew/2.7.html">Frontpage</a><br>
       <span class="linkdescr">or <a href="whatsnew/index.html">all "What's new" documents</a> since 2.0</span></p>
